==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Handball
<hw>Hand"ball`</hw> <pr>(h⟦acr⟧nd"b⟦add⟧l`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A small ball, usually made of rubber, thrown or struck
with the hand in various games.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A game played with such a ball, as by players
striking it to and fro between them with the hands, or, when played in a
walled court or against a single wall, striking it in turns against a
wall, until one side or the other fails to return the ball.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Handbarrow</ent>⟦br⟧
